 His passing in eMalahleni’s Cosmos Hospital early Saturday morning, was met with shock and sadness. Hundreds of messages flooded Middelburg Observer social media platforms after his passing, and the paper would like to afford the community an opportunity to have their stories and memories about Dr Keys published in this week’s edition of the paper. Short messages can be forwarded to gerhard@mobserver.co.za Messages that aren’t featured in the paper, will be published online. • Dr. Cecil Keys was een van die dorp se bekendste en geliefste dokters. Sy afserwe in eMalahleni se Kosmos Hospitaal vroeg Saterdagmore, is begroet met skok en hartseer. Honderde boodskappe is na sy dood op Middelburg Observer sosiale media platforms gedeel en die koerant bied die gemeenskap die geleentheid om hul stories en herinneringe van dr. Keys die week te publiseer. Kort boodskappe kan gestuur word na gerhard@mobserver.co.za Boodskappe wat nie in die koerant verskyn nie, word aanlyn gepubliseer.